latestPosts.caption:
Not sure what I did right but, the amount of blessings God has sent my way has been beyond my wildest dreams. Truly, I did not have this in my bingo card this year. 🥹

When choosing my quote I genuinely was so stuck. All that came to mind was that I wouldn’t be exactly where I am today without my family. My parents consistently telling me “Échale ganas”  at EVERY stage in my life. I can honestly say because of their encouragement I’ve kept going hoping one day I’d find my path. So cheers to those who lift us up because without them it be so easy to give up. 🤍🥂

Also shoutout to my sweet hubby for hyping me up and also being there every step of the way. I downplay a lot of my successes and he’s always there to help me snap out of that mindset. ILY @myagentraul 

#hispanicheritagemonth #latinacreators #sephorasquad

Still can’t believe this night was real!! Make the vision board, post the video, the time is NOW. 

When I started creating content in 2021, I made a vision board and on it I put that I wanted to meet Rihanna / work with her on a campaign. THEN when I got Sephora squad I was so excited & thought maybe this will be my way to meet Rihanna. 🥹

Also - she causally hung out in our little circle and told @itsbrandyncross that his eye makeup was irritatingly good!! 😂
